All Implemented Interfaces:
TreeVisitor<Void,Void>
public class LinearVisitor
extends BaseTypeVisitor<Void,Void>

A type-checking visitor for the Linear type system. The visitor reports an error ("unsafe.use") for any use of a reference of Unusable type. In other words, it reports an error for any Linear references that is used more than once, or is used after it has been "used up".
